Ext.data.JsonP['Proxy_Properties']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Proxy Properties</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n\t\t<div id=\"banner\" class=\"confbox admonition admonition-note aui-message warning shadowed information-macro\">\n\t\t\t<p>You can now find Appcelerator documentation at <a href=\"https://docs.axway.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.axway.com/</a>. This site will be taken down in the near future.</p>\n\t\t</div>\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-41845767\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Proxy Properties</h1>\n    <p>    <span style=\"color: #484848;\">\nDemonstrates expressing properties of Titanium objects with Alloy proxy elements.    </span>\n    <span style=\"color: #484848;\">\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <div class=\"confbox admonition admonition-info aui-message hint shadowed information-macro has-no-icon\">\n            <div class=\"title\">App Folder Location</div>\n            <p>alloy/test/apps/<strong class=\" \">ui/proxy_properties</strong>    </p>\n    </div>\n        <p>    <span style=\"color: #484848;\">\n<br>    </br></span>\nMany Titanium UI objects and properties can be declared in Alloy as mark-up. These mark-up elements are considered proxies for the underlying Titanium APIs. For example, the <a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Proxy_Properties-section-src-41845767_ProxyProperties-ios\">views/ios/index.xml</a> view, shown below, uses the following proxies.    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.iOS.NavigationWindow\">&lt;NavigationWindow/&gt;</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.Window\">&lt;Window/&gt;</a>    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.Window-property-leftNavButton\">&lt;LeftNavButton/&gt;</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.Window-property-rightNavButton\">&lt;RightNavButton/&gt;</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.Window-property-titleControl\">&lt;TitleControl/&gt;</a>    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.Button\">&lt;Button/&gt;</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.TextField\">&lt;TextField/&gt;</a>    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.TextField-property-leftButton\">&lt;LeftButton/&gt;</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.TextField-property-rightButton\">&lt;RightButton/&gt;</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.TextField-property-keyboardToolbar\">&lt;KeyboardToolbar/&gt;</a>    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.iOS.Toolbar\">&lt;Toolbar/&gt;</a>    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.iOS.Toolbar-property-items\">&lt;Items/&gt;</a>    </p>\n</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul>    <p>Proxies that represent properties of objects are nested inside the parent element. For example, a <a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.Window\">&lt;Window/&gt;</a> element&apos;s <a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.Window-property-leftNavButton\">leftNavProperty</a> is represented by a <a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.Window-property-leftNavButton\">&lt;LeftNavButton/&gt;</a> child element. Proxies can nest multiple levels, as shown with the Toolbar element in the XML view below.    </p>\n    <p>    <span id=\"src-41845767_ProxyProperties-ios\"><a class=\"confluence-anchor-link\" name=\"src-41845767_ProxyProperties-ios\"/></span>\n    </p>\n    <div class=\"confbox programlisting defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\">\n                    <div class=\"title\">views/ios/index.xml</div>\n                <div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" class=\"defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\" data-title=\"views/ios/index.xml\">\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">&lt;Alloy&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">  &lt;NavigationWindow&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;Window&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;!-- proxy properties </code><code class=\"keyword\">for</code><code class=\"plain\"> the window --&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;LeftNavButton&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">        &lt;Button onClick=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;sayHi&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;say hi&lt;/Button&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;/LeftNavButton&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;TitleControl&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">        &lt;Label&gt;title control&lt;/Label&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;/TitleControl&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;RightNavButton&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">        &lt;Button onClick=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;doAlert&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;alert&lt;/Button&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;/RightNavButton&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;!-- test rest of the Window markup --&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;Require src=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;table&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;!-- iOS TextField proxy properties --&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;TextField id=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;textfield&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\"> platform=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;ios&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">        &lt;LeftButton&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">          &lt;Button onClick=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;sayHi&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\"> </code><code class=\"keyword\">class</code><code class=\"plain\">=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;textButton&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;left&lt;/Button&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">        &lt;/LeftButton&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">        &lt;RightButton&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">          &lt;Button onClick=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;doAlert&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\"> </code><code class=\"keyword\">class</code><code class=\"plain\">=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;textButton&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;right&lt;/Button&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">        &lt;/RightButton&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">        &lt;!-- even nested proxy properties --&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">        &lt;KeyboardToolbar&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">          &lt;Toolbar&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">            &lt;Items&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">              &lt;Button&gt;button </code><code class=\"value\">1</code><code class=\"plain\">&lt;/Button&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">              &lt;FlexSpace/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">              &lt;Button&gt;button </code><code class=\"value\">2</code><code class=\"plain\">&lt;/Button&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">            &lt;/Items&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">          &lt;/Toolbar&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">        &lt;/KeyboardToolbar&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;/TextField&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;/Window&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">  &lt;/NavigationWindow&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">&lt;/Alloy&gt;</code></div>\n</div>\n    </div>\n    <p>The views/table.xml view defines a &lt;<a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.TableView\">TableView</a>/&gt; element and various properties of the TableView such as its footerView and headerView, as well as <a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.TableViewSection\">TableViewSection</a> and TableViewRow elements.    </p>\n    <div class=\"confbox programlisting defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\">\n                    <div class=\"title\">views/table.xml</div>\n                <div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" class=\"defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\" data-title=\"views/table.xml\">\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">&lt;Alloy&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">  &lt;TableView id=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;table&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;!-- proxy properties </code><code class=\"keyword\">for</code><code class=\"plain\"> the table --&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;HeaderView&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;View id=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;headerView&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;/HeaderView&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;HeaderPullView&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;View id=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;headerPull&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">        &lt;Label id=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;pullLabel&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;Would be refreshing...&lt;/Label&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;/View&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;/HeaderPullView&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;FooterView&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;View id=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;footerView&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;/FooterView&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;TableViewSection headerTitle=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;section 1&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;TableViewRow title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;row 1&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;TableViewRow title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;row 2&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;TableViewRow title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;row 3&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;TableViewRow title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;row 4&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;TableViewRow title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;row 5&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;/TableViewSection&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;TableViewSection&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;HeaderView&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">        &lt;Label height=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;30dp&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\"> backgroundColor=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;#ff0&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;section </code><code class=\"value\">2</code><code class=\"plain\">&lt;/Label&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;/HeaderView&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;FooterView&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">        &lt;Label height=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;30dp&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\"> backgroundColor=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;#0ff&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;the footer&lt;/Label&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;/FooterView&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;TableViewRow title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;row 1&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;TableViewRow title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;row 2&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;TableViewRow title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;row 3&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;TableViewRow title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;row 4&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;TableViewRow title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;row 5&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;/TableViewSection&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">  &lt;/TableView&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">&lt;/Alloy&gt;</code></div>\n</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-41845767_ProxyProperties-SeeAlso\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>See Also</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link unresolved\" href=\"#!/guide/Proxy_Properties-section-src-41845767\">Proxy Properties</a>    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=41845767\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Proxy Properties"});